    <div class="col-lg-9">
      <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold text-success mb-5 text-center">Privacy Policy</h1>

      <div class="bg-dark p-5 rounded shadow">
        <p class="text-muted small mb-5 text-center">
          Last updated: March 23, 2026
        </p>

        <h4 class="mb-4">1. Introduction</h4>
        <p class="text-muted mb-5">
          Welcome to ResumeForge AI. We are committed to protecting your privacy and handling your personal information responsibly.<br>
          This Privacy Policy explains what information we collect, how we use it, and how we protect it when you use our website and services.
        </p>

        <h4 class="mb-4">2. Information We Collect</h4>
        <p class="text-muted mb-4">We collect the following types of information:</p>
        <ul class="text-muted mb-5 ms-4">
          <li><strong>Uploaded files</strong> (resumes, PDFs, TXT files) — processed temporarily for analysis and deleted immediately after use.</li>
          <li><strong>Job descriptions</strong> — pasted text you provide during optimization.</li>
          <li><strong>LinkedIn profile sections</strong> — text you voluntarily paste (headline, about, experience, skills).</li>
          <li><strong>Technical data</strong> — IP address, browser type, device info (standard server logs).</li>
          <li><strong>No account data</strong> — we do not require sign-up, email, or passwords at this time.</li>
        </ul>

        <h4 class="mb-4">3. How We Use Your Information</h4>
        <ul class="text-muted mb-5 ms-4">
          <li>To provide the resume optimization, cover letter generation, and LinkedIn profile suggestion services.</li>
          <li>To improve our AI models and user experience (anonymized and aggregated only).</li>
          <li>To debug and maintain the service.</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-muted mb-5">
          <strong>We do NOT</strong> sell your personal information, use it for advertising, or share it with third parties except as required by law.
        </p>

        <h4 class="mb-4">4. Data Storage & Deletion</h4>
        <p class="text-muted mb-5">
          All uploaded files and input text are:
          <br>• Processed in memory or temporarily on disk
          <br>• Deleted automatically within seconds after processing
          <br>• Never stored long-term or in databases
        </p>

        <h4 class="mb-4">5. Third-Party Services</h4>
        <p class="text-muted mb-5">
          We use the following external AI providers to power our features:
          <ul class="ms-4">
            <li>Groq (Llama models)</li>
            <li>Google Gemini</li>
            <li>OpenRouter</li>
          </ul>
          These providers receive only the text you submit for analysis. They are bound by their own privacy policies and do not receive any identifying information about you.
        </p>

        <h4 class="mb-4">6. Security</h4>
        <p class="text-muted mb-5">
          We implement reasonable security measures to protect the temporary data we process.<br>
          However, no method of transmission over the internet is 100% secure — use the service accordingly.
        </p>

        <h4 class="mb-4">7. Your Rights</h4>
        <p class="text-muted mb-5">
          Because we do not store personal data long-term, there is no profile or account to access, correct, or delete.<br>
          If you have concerns about any temporary data processed during your session, contact us immediately.
        </p>

        <h4 class="mb-4">8. Changes to This Policy</h4>
        <p class="text-muted mb-5">
          We may update this policy occasionally. Changes will be posted here with an updated "last updated" date.
